# Compiled output of the workspace packages (server / lib / contract prototype).
# The client depends on `arkade-coinflip` (packages/lib) for the coinflip-escrow
# CONTRACT exports; with `transpileDependencies` the symlinked dist/*.js lands
# inside the project tree and the vue-cli eslint plugin would otherwise lint
# transpiled JS (var / require()). These are build artifacts, not source.
packages/**/dist/
